
  1.0 (1/2/2004)

     * Added Search for User functionality (linking to [1]directory
       services plugin, a Squirrelmail plugin that implements LDAP
       directory search, with javascript)
     * Added Email Notification functionality; useracl can now send an
       email to the 'recipient' of the ACL, to notify her of the changes
       in her permissions.
     * Update all == adds new username as well
     * Added icons in the user interface, which can enabled optionally.
     * Fixed miscellaneous bugs.
     * Implemented 'addacl' link from Directory Result search page.
       (Experimental)
     * Plugin is now up to current Squirrelmail standards - small and
       fast setup.php, versioning information.

  0.9 (19/11/2003)

     * Initial Version.

References

   1. http://email.uoa.gr/projects/squirrelmail/directory.php
